snippet.title: Game boy Longplay [252] Snoopy's Magic Show
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Mariofan98

Snoopys Magic Show is an Action puzzle video game based on the Snoopy cartoon characters licensed from Peanuts.
It was developed and published by Kemco, which was released for the Game Boy in 1990.

The player controls Snoopy who has to save four Woodstocks,
within a fixed amount of time, by dodging bouncing balls, pushing blocks, using warp zones and power-ups.
There are 120 levels (first 60 normal and then again abit harder) with a unique password to access each.

Awesome game for the european launch year of the Game Boy.

7/10 -
